Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.14,0:07:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,下回 VS哈薩卡篇
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.48,0:07:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother ***ker
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.63,0:07:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotcha
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.21,0:07:53.99,Default,,0,0,0,,感覺不錯 這個rap一定能把會長的心意傳達到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.84,0:07:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎
