Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.45,0:11:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,不斷進步 不會停下腳步
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.48,0:11:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,這就是我的non fiction
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.21,0:11:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah
